.git
.github
.githooks
.gitignore
.dockerignore
Dockerfile
*.md
# Exclude docs/ from build contexts EXCEPT the one brand asset the n8n image bakes in
# as the node icon (docs/assets/logo-face.svg). Spelled out so a parent-dir exclusion
# does not mask the re-include.
docs/*
!docs/assets
docs/assets/*
!docs/assets/logo-face.svg
testdata/
**/*_test.go
crawl.private/
# n8n package build artifacts — must never overlay the in-image frozen install when the
# n8n image builds from this (repo-root) context.
**/node_modules/
integrations/n8n/dist/
integrations/n8n/.pnpm-store/
